title: It took 75 governors to elect a woman. Spanberger will soon be at Virginia's helm
description: Abigail Spanberger, a former CIA officer and three-term congresswoman, is breaking long-held traditions on inauguration day. She says she wants her swearing-in to showcase the state's modern vibrancy.
